{"tid":510803,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠咗兩年","createTime":"2017-12-26T22:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T22:24:50.000Z","uid":113365,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5b492641ae75e1a24aed381b456d6166b3758d0f","tid":510803,"uid":113365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:46:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線由考完dse後就失眠咗兩年，到以家老豆老母都係以為我打機打得多先咁，叫我咪撚阻住地球轉。由以前訓八個鐘後暈暈地，到前排考試無一晚訓得入，以家就由12點係張床碌到1點然後4點醒咗訓唔返<br />\n<br />\n以家無一刻個腦會休息到，就算失眠朝早都係訓唔入，好驚遲早變弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗嘢同做嘢嘅反應都慢咗好多，加上失眠令到個人好暴燥，試過因為四五點失眠開燈溫書嘈醒咗老母，同佢嘈到差啲想摑佢一巴，好彩理智仲控制得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢兩年嚟都係失住眠咁過，真正訓過嘅日子可能都唔夠半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每晚訓上床都好有壓力，每晚12點磨到2-3點先訓得入，跟住6-7點又要侷住醒，食過安眠藥訓真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但停藥個日即刻訓唔返，買過啲褪黑激素,雞精，都係冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排打工還學費又搞到無錢睇醫生，慘過死"},{"pid":"77294ca5e3a8211bde220fe9dc003799519e490d","tid":510803,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:48:01.000Z","msg":"做運動"},{"pid":"a1b719ad572e8ea9039b246faf5cc7f43e9f0c68","tid":510803,"uid":24752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:48:52.000Z","msg":"巴打有無睇醫生?"},{"pid":"2c78cdd9acafa10ea22c24d169ea208f86d0bb54","tid":510803,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f008a0bea6045372bddb583c6b6ca0d3add16d2b","tid":510803,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:09:26.000Z","msg":"雞精安眠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16d6eca49acddf90921b3ce169d5738dfeb2110","tid":510803,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:11:13.000Z","msg":"做看更啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓唔著唔好浪費"},{"pid":"1966148b9f126cf8ee992004ee90c6bc7268c823","tid":510803,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c78cdd9acafa10ea22c24d169ea208f86d0bb54","tid":510803,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"打夠20個"},{"pid":"92533dc82c8176a51c64e37ad4b615f9681a0613","tid":510803,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  考完dse到而家每一晚一係瞓唔着一係瞓得勁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f308209f018ceef82ebbbfd9c27d0d2e72a00ce","tid":510803,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"心魔<br />\n唔好依賴隻約<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有親人食左20年安眠藥<br />\n無晒工作能力<br />\n由一粒食到14粒<br />\n食到中風，家陣一粒都唔食訓十幾個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢仲以為d 血壓藥係安眠藥。<br />\n<br />\n你逾緊張訓唔著就逾難訓，你要搵出心魔，一驚就訓唔著"},{"pid":"b8f5789291d83f02e7d75e2417e349991859eddd","tid":510803,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"有d人訓三四個鐘都夠，唔洗唔緊張最重要係醒左既精神狀態如何"},{"pid":"9facb4aa6eac330a0a8bf719425d150b9cd0b6e3","tid":510803,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"你要正視問題 <br />\n愈早醫愈易醫 <br />\n快d睇醫生"},{"pid":"5d4e39567893392680a7b49b7b98d4710b9fbe24","tid":510803,"uid":113365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有無睇醫生?</blockquote><br />\n無錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過聽你哋咁講我都有啲想去睇下大學啲獸醫睇下有冇用"},{"pid":"3a2a4663879c962280bcd296fd80b907a4580a79","tid":510803,"uid":113365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:45:06.000Z","msg":"屌我老母叫我返多兩份pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攰啲就訓得入<br />\n<br />\n點解我老母咁黑心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我試過返到1點先返到屋企，第二朝六點出門口返工，兩晚都訓唔撚入<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfdb38c18b4456bfb00ad79fbda746c1768c043","tid":510803,"uid":65503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"我之前果幾年都係錦，宜家好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d016d02e3ec00ebbf29d2956f78b9981f327b573","tid":510803,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"巴打見你好辛苦喎 想瞓又唔瞓到 生活啲節奏都亂哂 仲影響埋讀書 加試屋企又畀咗你咁大壓力 一啲都唔體諒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你之前係自己買安眠藥？睇醫生食藥都係正路嘅 不過我諗可能心情都有啲影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afed912e0bb5679564cf214b6e3cbe48fb7421e3","tid":510803,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"買本書自學催眠<br />\n<br />\n利申：成功例子"},{"pid":"fcdb7b933d1ff97e859fad6efb1c794466d6687f","tid":510803,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32d83ba1f28b36ee6ef7966f3dc9b20ba07ee34","tid":510803,"uid":94157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"我都有失眠問題，我係好快訓倒，不過四五個鐘之後要醒，好難訓得番。"},{"pid":"aa4b55333596a573c443c309b8c0c421251ca6df","tid":510803,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"我琴晚都訓唔着,一個月有一星期都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b984fbca6bacd45046f1b144d02c9d49a74562","tid":510803,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f308209f018ceef82ebbbfd9c27d0d2e72a00ce","tid":510803,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"心魔<br />\n唔好依賴隻約<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有親人食左20年安眠藥<br />\n無晒工作能力<br />\n由一粒食到14粒<br />\n食到中風，家陣一粒都唔食訓十幾個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢仲以為d 血壓藥係安眠藥。<br />\n<br />\n你逾緊張訓唔著就逾難訓，你要搵出心魔，一驚就訓唔著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"你親人自己買安眠藥食？<br />\n<br />\n你睇精神科 佢應該會教<br />\n每日一粒份量 唔可以連續食多過14日<br />\n每14日要停7日<br />\n<br />\n我都長期失眠<br />\n跟佢pattern食都食左幾年<br />\n呢家慢慢減到得返4分1粒"},{"pid":"a1fdceef59dc8157f3cc98bd3be07dd1ebe5f02f","tid":510803,"uid":129304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"代表你進化緊做新類型人，好事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1e5c50806541277aa6ba806dad7a1305e97702","tid":510803,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:05:41.000Z","msg":"關唔關茶同咖啡事?<br />\n<br />\n留意下飲野啦<br />\n<br />\n一係睇睇中醫"},{"pid":"949063196d3b533b4c64f07d272d50b2c9a1d3e7","tid":510803,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾醫生, 真想去屌佢"},{"pid":"9db642833f091eec89fd8d42648990718f7e0032","tid":510803,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"失眠有好多成因<br />\n巴打試試做運動？<br />\n我以前失眠都係靠做運動 始終食藥對身體無咁好<br />\n同埋你夠膽的話可以搵下教psychology嘅professor傾下 佢地會有專業知識 又好人 加上唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543df0782148d09eaee582220556bf3ed65364f6","tid":510803,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"我好你少少，叫瞓得着，但睡眠質素好差，成日發夢好似無瞓過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}